00:48:56.300 --> 00:48:57.301 align:middle line:90%
to it.

00:48:57.301 --> 00:48:58.670 align:middle line:84%
>> Lisa: Or the karma
of the people

00:48:58.670 --> 00:49:00.104 align:middle line:84%
that the collective people that
