00:49:34.939 --> 00:49:38.142 align:middle line:84%
Let me sum up exactly how
you break the cycle of karma,

00:49:38.142 --> 00:49:39.477 align:middle line:84%
or actually would
you sum that up.

00:49:39.477 --> 00:49:41.212 align:middle line:90%
How do you do that?

00:49:41.212 --> 00:49:44.148 align:middle line:84%
Letting go, being
aware of it, what else?

00:49:44.148 --> 00:49:45.883 align:middle line:84%
>> Nunziata: Ultimately,
you have to allow yourself

00:49:45.883 --> 00:49:48.453 align:middle line:84%
to feel the feeling that
you've been resisting.

00:49:48.453 --> 00:49:51.923 align:middle line:84%
So if I am feeling unloved
I have to feel that.

00:49:51.923 --> 00:49:54.525 align:middle line:84%
If I'm feeling guilty,
as we talked about before

00:49:54.525 --> 00:49:57.562 align:middle line:84%
with the approval-seeking
thing, you doing me a favor

00:49:57.562 --> 00:49:58.796 align:middle line:90%
or not doing me a favor.

00:49:58.796 --> 00:50:03.000 align:middle line:84%
So once, as I allow myself
to feel the feeling,

00:50:03.000 --> 00:50:06.204 align:middle line:90%
the emotion dissolves.

00:50:06.204 --> 00:50:08.072 align:middle line:90%
But this is hard to do.

00:50:08.072 --> 00:50:09.307 align:middle line:84%
>> Lisa: Well, to
be aware of it.

00:50:09.307 --> 00:50:12.510 align:middle line:84%
So say in a relationship
and a couple got a divorce,

00:50:12.510 --> 00:50:15.680 align:middle line:84%
did they complete that
karma by getting the divorce

00:50:15.680 --> 00:50:19.550 align:middle line:84%
or will they only do that
as they get into the feeling

00:50:19.550 --> 00:50:21.352 align:middle line:84%
of the reason why
the divorce happened,

00:50:21.352 --> 00:50:24.689 align:middle line:84%
and then they can start to
resolve and create newly.

00:50:24.689 --> 00:50:25.890 align:middle line:90%
>> Nunziata: Right.

00:50:25.890 --> 00:50:27.692 align:middle line:84%
So we have people who get
married multiple times,

00:50:27.692 --> 00:50:30.595 align:middle line:84%
they can't -- because they
never cleared the energy.

00:50:30.595 --> 00:50:34.065 align:middle line:84%
So if I get a divorce and it's
been an enlightening experience,

00:50:34.065 --> 00:50:38.302 align:middle line:84%
and I realize okay, this
is not what I wanted,

00:50:38.302 --> 00:50:41.572 align:middle line:84%
and I went through the
emotion of that divorce,

00:50:41.572 --> 00:50:43.407 align:middle line:90%
and I understand what happened.

00:50:43.407 --> 00:50:46.377 align:middle line:84%
Now I can go out and
create a better relationship

00:50:46.377 --> 00:50:48.112 align:middle line:90%
or attract the right person.

00:50:48.112 --> 00:50:49.514 align:middle line:90%
If I don't --

00:50:49.514 --> 00:50:50.414 align:middle line:84%
>> Lisa: You're going
to keep creating it over

00:50:50.414 --> 00:50:51.249 align:middle line:90%
and over and over again --

00:50:51.249 --> 00:50:52.450 align:middle line:90%
>> Nunziata: Same exact thing.

00:50:52.450 --> 00:50:53.751 align:middle line:84%
>> Lisa: Which is exactly
