00:51:06.697 --> 00:51:08.332 align:middle line:90%
to specific karma with somebody.

00:51:08.332 --> 00:51:09.934 align:middle line:90%
From a past life.

00:51:09.934 --> 00:51:11.736 align:middle line:84%
>> Nunziata: And that
is part of it as well,

00:51:11.736 --> 00:51:14.038 align:middle line:84%
because you will bring people
