00:51:14.038 --> 00:51:16.641 align:middle line:84%
from past lifetimes and
resolve relationships

00:51:16.641 --> 00:51:17.542 align:middle line:90%
with them from the past.

00:51:17.542 --> 00:51:19.410 align:middle line:90%
Those are all elements of karma.

