Most of the families and
close people you encounter

00:51:31.022 --> 00:51:32.557 align:middle line:84%
in your life that
you've had some kind

00:51:32.557 --> 00:51:33.925 align:middle line:90%
of history with them somewhere.

00:51:33.925 --> 00:51:35.860 align:middle line:84%
>> Lisa: Or not so close,
work relationships, bosses.

00:51:35.860 --> 00:51:36.494 align:middle line:90%
>> Nunziata: Right.

00:51:36.494 --> 00:51:37.895 align:middle line:90%
Could be anybody.

00:51:37.895 --> 00:51:39.063 align:middle line:84%
Yeah. People that you have had
some kind of experience with.

00:51:39.063 --> 00:51:40.464 align:middle line:84%
>> Lisa: Let me ask
you that for a second.

00:51:40.464 --> 00:51:43.668 align:middle line:84%
If you have a boss that you
