that contention brings up

00:51:47.138 --> 00:51:50.374 align:middle line:84%
and you're likely to find the
karmic relationship there.

00:51:50.374 --> 00:51:52.143 align:middle line:84%
Sit with the feelings
and they'll dissolve.

00:51:52.143 --> 00:51:53.477 align:middle line:84%
>> Nunziata: So I had a woman,
I'll give you an example

00:51:53.477 --> 00:51:55.246 align:middle line:90%
because you're using a boss.

00:51:55.246 --> 00:51:57.748 align:middle line:84%
Comes to me, tells me she
has this abusive boss,

00:51:57.748 --> 00:52:00.051 align:middle line:84%
and the guy is yelling at her
to make her feel terrible, blah,

00:52:00.051 --> 00:52:02.019 align:middle line:84%
blah, blah, and as
I start talking

00:52:02.019 --> 00:52:04.422 align:middle line:84%
to her all she did
was defend the boss.

00:52:04.422 --> 00:52:05.556 align:middle line:84%
Well, he's under
a lot of pressure,

00:52:05.556 --> 00:52:07.091 align:middle line:90%
and this is what's going on.

00:52:07.091 --> 00:52:09.060 align:middle line:84%
So as we did the work and I
said what are you feeling.

00:52:09.060 --> 00:52:11.295 align:middle line:90%
Well, I feel unappreciated.

00:52:11.295 --> 00:52:12.997 align:middle line:84%
I really feel like he doesn't
appreciate the work I do.

00:52:12.997 --> 00:52:14.198 align:middle line:84%
So who made you feel
unappreciated?

00:52:14.198 --> 00:52:15.299 align:middle line:90%
My father.

00:52:15.299 --> 00:52:15.866 align:middle line:90%
Who's the boss?

00:52:15.866 --> 00:52:16.767 align:middle line:90%
Your father.

00:52:16.767 --> 00:52:17.568 align:middle line:90%
So what did you do?

00:52:17.568 --> 00:52:19.270 align:middle line:90%
You brought your father in,

00:52:19.270 --> 00:52:22.139 align:middle line:84%
because your father made you
feel unappreciated.

00:52:22.139 --> 00:52:24.408 align:middle line:84%
You didn't process that feeling,
so you brought your boss in,

00:52:24.408 --> 00:52:26.177 align:middle line:84%
and you did exactly the
same thing when I asked you

00:52:26.177 --> 00:52:28.145 align:middle line:90%
about your father, defended him.

00:52:28.145 --> 00:52:29.714 align:middle line:84%
>> Lisa: So then
what, she realized it?

00:52:29.714 --> 00:52:31.249 align:middle line:84%
>> Nunziata: So she
worked through the feeling

00:52:31.249 --> 00:52:32.183 align:middle line:90%
of being unappreciated.

00:52:32.183 --> 00:52:33.651 align:middle line:90%
Now here's what happened.

00:52:33.651 --> 00:52:34.685 align:middle line:90%
This was the miraculous thing.

00:52:34.685 --> 00:52:37.755 align:middle line:84%
A few months later
she said to me -- we had

00:52:37.755 --> 00:52:39.757 align:middle line:84%
finished doing the work, and I
still kept in contact with her,

00:52:39.757 --> 00:52:42.226 align:middle line:84%
she said you're not going
believe what happened.

00:52:42.226 --> 00:52:44.262 align:middle line:90%
He got transferred.

00:52:44.262 --> 00:52:45.296 align:middle line:90%
>> Lisa: Interesting.

00:52:45.296 --> 00:52:46.397 align:middle line:90%
Interesting.

00:52:46.397 --> 00:52:48.599 align:middle line:84%
>> Nunziata: So once
she cleared the energy,

00:52:48.599 --> 00:52:51.802 align:middle line:84%
her soul said you don't
need to do this anymore.

00:52:51.802 --> 00:52:54.639 align:middle line:84%
So your soul will resolve it,
because your soul will say okay,

00:52:54.639 --> 00:52:56.741 align:middle line:84%
