person will be gone

00:52:56.741 --> 00:52:58.776 align:middle line:84%
or the other person will come
in, or whatever has to happen.

00:52:58.776 --> 00:53:00.077 align:middle line:90%
>> Lisa: And most likely in that

00:53:00.077 --> 00:53:02.647 align:middle line:84%
circumstance she will then
create more opportunities.

00:53:02.647 --> 00:53:05.416 align:middle line:84%
>> Nunziata: Or attract
a much better situation,

00:53:05.416 --> 00:53:07.652 align:middle line:84%
or a boss that makes
