00:53:07.652 --> 00:53:10.254 align:middle line:84%
and the work she's
doing it valuable.

00:53:10.254 --> 00:53:12.356 align:middle line:84%
But it -- she didn't do
it -- she said you know,

00:53:12.356 --> 00:53:14.125 align:middle line:84%
I didn't do anything,
but she really did,

00:53:14.125 --> 00:53:15.593 align:middle line:90%
she did it with herself.

00:53:15.593 --> 00:53:17.161 align:middle line:84%
She said I didn't do
anything with him.

00:53:17.161 --> 00:53:18.562 align:middle line:90%
>> Lisa: That's a great example.

00:53:18.562 --> 00:53:19.664 align:middle line:90%
That's a perfect example.

